Continuous Improvement Focus:

Prompt Evolution: Continuously refine prompts to capture evolving language patterns and improve metric accuracy.

Contextual Awareness: Enhance the evaluation's ability to understand nuanced contexts.

Deeper Semantic Relevance Checks: Introduce advanced semantic similarity techniques.

Dynamic Benchmarking: Update benchmarks based on new data and user feedback.

Cross-Metric Consistency Analysis: Ensure scoring consistency across different metrics over time.

Real-time Feedback Loop: Incorporate real-time user feedback for continuous learning and adaptation.
